{"type": "article", "id": 16688, "title": "Snail Haptor USB", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-28T06:14:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 144, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125502zcQhHbWCTIp1kDPK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款多功能的数据线，线上布满了具有吸附功能的圆点，能将这条数据线像卷尺一样固定在一起。放在包里就不会相互缠绕，而且非常容易找到。将有圆点的一侧贴在桌面上立起来也是一个手机的支撑，即便是在光滑的平面上也能稳定的固定住。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144001LXGUpaiowE5fNBrO.jpg\" width=\"428\" height=\"483\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.12850467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144002ntC1JOk9PE4LqWSv.jpg\" width=\"475\" height=\"483\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.01684211\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144003Ewl8WbzZ2QITuFpm.jpg\" width=\"383\" height=\"483\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.26109661\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}